ngine already gives Black a winning edge! Here's now the game may finish:} ({Nxb7? Bxb7 (or Ng4 first with the same idea.) Rxb7} 19... Ng4 20. h3 fxg3 $1 {The key intermezzo, White can't take on g4 due to mate on h2 !} 21. fxg3 Qe3+ 22. Kh1 Nf2+ 23. Rxf2 Rxf2 {with a winning position.}) *

