he center and protect our knight. Black has many other good moves as well.} 8. e3 Ne4 {The knights dominate the center and poor queen is running out of squares.} 9. Qd3 Nc5 10. Qc3 Ndb3 {It's clear that Black is totally winning now.} 11. Qxe5+ Qe7 12. Qxg7 Rf8 13. Rb1 Qe4 {And White will lose the rook and the game.} *

