tronger players know about the ... h6 & ... g5 trap. White intends to play a3 and take back on c3 with the bishop.} O-O {Black's most natural move. We anticipate a3 and get ready to execute our central break plan with ... Re8 and ... e5 next.} 7. a3 Bxc3 8. Bxc3 Re8 ({This is a big improvement over the original book recommendation of} 8... Qe7 {. While the idea is the same, to play for the ... e5 push, I believe it's more accurate to start with Re8 , as we will see.}) 9. e3 {White is getting ready to develop their LSB and castle kingside. But our plan is very simple: the ... e5 pawn push!} e5 {Black executes the key strategic idea of this opening. We create a nice pawn chain: c7 - d6 - e5 and open up our LSB.} 10. d5 {This is the ambitious option, but we don't mind the closed nature of the resulting positions, since we have the knights vs the bishop pair.} Ne7 {We often retreat the knight to b8 in order to reroute it to c5 , but since White always has b4 ready, we shift our focus to undermining the d5 - & c4 -pawns with either ... c6 or ... b5 .} 11. e4 {A logical move, White completes the central grip grabbing more space. However, White's kingside is still not fully developed and we use the time to undermine White's center.} c6 {An instructive idea and a strong novelty, chipping away at White's strong center!} 12. Be2 {A logical move. White is getting ready to complete their development with O-O next.} Ng6 {The knight is aiming for the f4 -outpost.} 13. O-O Nf4 {Black's knight is a monster on f4 . The closed nature of this position makes White's bishop pair irrelevant.} 14. Rfe1 Bg4 {We complete our development and put extra pressure on the f3 -knight.} 15. Bd1 b5 {I like this cool idea of taking advantage of White's poor coordination. This is a fun position for us to play, and White can easily go wrong.} 16. dxc6 (16. cxb5 cxd5 17. exd5 N6xd5) 16... bxc4 17. Qa4 Qb6 18. Qxc4 Rac8 19. Ba4 {Too greedy.} Bxf3 20. gxf3 {White's kingside is now permanently ruined.} N6h5 {Black will follow up with ... Re6 and has a big attack.} *

