{Conclusion: The Blackmar-Diemer Gambit is not quite sound, but accuracy is required from Black.  Surprise White with my recommended Bf5! and watch their reaction.  Active play and hidden tactics lurk in the position, and, if you study the lines well, you will be the one crushing your opponent in this one!} 1. Z0 *

