dy to meet b4 with ... Nxd5 and ... Nxb4 .} 12. Nf4 hxg3 13. hxg3 Bg4 {I prefer Black here since we have a clear plan, attack the king on the h-file. The engine agrees giving us a solid -0.8 edge.} *

