e finish development and give White a choice to trade the queen for two rooks. Also strong is} 12... Rf8 $5) 13. Qg5 {This is the only move to stay in the game.} Qxg5 ({The simple choice. We can also go for complications with} 13... Qxc2 14. Bxh8 {, but White holds with best play.}) 14. fxg5 d4 {It's clear that Black is having all the fun in this endgame, just compare the rooks for both sides! We will play for attack while it's hard for White to finish development.} *

